g> the Oldlake Stalker in this PS1 style horror game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first horror game made by LunaApps which features an interactive environment and creepy characters while you survive an escape room puzzle and explore the convenience store.</p>",
